<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "The Common Provenance Model Ontology (CPM-O) provides a formal, machine-actionable vocabulary for tracking the provenance of samples and data in multi-organizational environments."@en .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> "RNDr. Rudolf Wittner" .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-02-05"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Bc. Stanislav Prikryl"@en .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The normative OWL 2 ontology representing the Common Provenance Model (CPM). It is designed to support the traceability of samples and data in multi-organizational environments, as defined by the Common Provenance Framework (CPF)."@en .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-17"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> <https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19889324> .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Common Provenance Model Ontology (CPM-O)"@en .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "cpm" .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#" .
<https://www.commonprovenancemodel.org/cpm#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://github.com/Common-Provenance-Framework> .
